  "detailed_description": "Connect all the dots of the same color to solve each level. <br />\r\nIf you overlap different colored line, the connection is lost.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSelect from simple 5x5 levels to difficult 10x10 levels.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUsing the included level editor, you can create levels up to 12x12 in size or customize existing ones and send them to someone else using the import/export function.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- More than 500 puzzles.<br />\r\n- 6 Levels of difficulty.<br />\r\n- Hint to solve the puzzle.<br />\r\n- Day / Night mode.<br />\r\n- Level editor with import / export!<br />\r\n- Sound effects of musical instruments.<br />\r\n- Minimalist graphic design.",
  "about_the_game": "Connect all the dots of the same color to solve each level. <br />\r\nIf you overlap different colored line, the connection is lost.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSelect from simple 5x5 levels to difficult 10x10 levels.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUsing the included level editor, you can create levels up to 12x12 in size or customize existing ones and send them to someone else using the import/export function.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- More than 500 puzzles.<br />\r\n- 6 Levels of difficulty.<br />\r\n- Hint to solve the puzzle.<br />\r\n- Day / Night mode.<br />\r\n- Level editor with import / export!<br />\r\n- Sound effects of musical instruments.<br />\r\n- Minimalist graphic design.",
